import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
from glob import glob
import os.path as osp
In [ ]:
for file in glob('/Users/gericovidanes/Library/CloudStorage/OneDrive-UniversityofSouthampton/2024_6DOF_FlightTests/*_6D.tsv'):
    print(file)
    
    group_num = osp.split(file)[1].split('_')[0][5:]
    print(group_num)

    df = pd.read_csv(file,sep='\t',skiprows=11)
    print(df.columns)

    gimbal_pos = df[['Gimbal1 X','Y','Z']].to_numpy()
    gimbal_rpy = df[['Roll','Pitch','Yaw']].to_numpy()
    if f'M{group_num} X' in df.columns:
        drone_pos = df[[f'M{group_num} X','Y.2','Z.2']].to_numpy()
        drone_rpy = df[['Roll.2','Pitch.2','Yaw.2']].to_numpy()

    fig, axs = plt.subplots(3,2, figsize=(12,8))

    labels = ['x','y','z']
    for i in range(3):
        if f'M{group_num} X' in df.columns:
            axs[i,0].plot(drone_pos[:,i], label=f'drone-{labels[i]}')
        axs[i,0].plot(gimbal_pos[:,i], label=f'gimbal-{labels[i]}')
        axs[i,0].legend()

    labels = ['roll', 'pitch', 'yaw']
    for i in range(3):
        if f'M{group_num} X' in df.columns:
            axs[i,1].plot(drone_rpy[:,i], label=f'drone-{labels[i]}')
        axs[i,1].plot(gimbal_rpy[:,i], label=f'gimbal-{labels[i]}')
        axs[i,1].legend()

    plt.show()
